Uses of Class
com.jakewharton.rxrelay2.Relay

    • Uses of Relay in com.jakewharton.rxrelay2

      Subclasses of Relay in com.jakewharton.rxrelay2 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  BehaviorRelay<T>
      Relay that emits the most recent item it has observed and all subsequent observed items to each subscribed Observer.
      class  PublishRelay<T>
      Relay that, once an Observer has subscribed, emits all subsequently observed items to the subscriber.
      class  ReplayRelay<T>
      Replays events to Observers.
      Methods in com.jakewharton.rxrelay2 that return Relay 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Relay<T> Relay.toSerialized()
      Wraps this Relay and serializes the calls to accept(T), making it thread-safe.
